  "title": "Chinese Banquet Junior Sous Chef",
  "description": "<p>As a Junior Sous Chef, you will be responsible for the following in our Chinese Banquet Kitchen:</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Is in charge of controlling, examining and tasting food in mis-en place being served to ensure a consistent standard is being served to our guests.</li>\n  <li>Assist and ensures the inter-department transfers market lists and employee schedules are done on time.</li>\n  <li>Ensure a high standard in presentation, variety and freshness in for all food production</li>\n  <li>Ensure restaurant and working areas are properly maintained and cleaned.</li>\n  <li>Is aware of cost control procedures, receipt development and ordering to insure freshness and preparation of all perishable items.</li>\n  <li>Ensures a professional attire and personal hygiene at all times.</li>\n  <li>Train and delegate tasks to part-time casual labour cooks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma, Bachelor's Degree/Post Graduate Diploma/Professional Degree in Food &amp; Beverage Services Management, Hospitality/Tourism/Hotel Management or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 3 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>\n  <li>Preferably Junior Executive specialized in Food/Beverage/Restaurant Service or equivalent</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Additional Information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5-day work week</li>\n  <li>13th month AWS and Performance Bonus</li>\n  <li>Annual Leave from 16 days</li>\n  <li>Up to 50% Associate Dining &amp; Accommodation Discounts at Group Properties</li>\n  <li>Referral Incentive of S$1,000*</li>\n  <li>Career Development and Training opportunities</li>\n</ul>\n<p>*Terms &amp; Conditions apply.</p>\n<p>PARKROYAL COLLECTION Marina Bay, Singapore is dedicated to providing equal employment opportunities, including individuals with disabilities.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
